uk.ac.manchester.cs.mekon.store.disk

Interface ICustomFrameMatcher

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ICustomValueMatcher

    public interface ICustomFrameMatcher
extends ICustomValueMatcher
    Interface whose implementations will provide customised query matching for specified frame-valued slot-types, to override the basic subsumption-based matching provided by the IMatcher implementations. For example, a particular implementation may provide matching based on aggregations over the values of one or more slots, with aggregate values specified via a designated query-only slot.
